data.description: Move-in ready, perfect for a starter home or to downsize, awaits you in the sought-after Ridge at Prairie View neighborhood! Upon arriving you are greeted by the charming covered front porch, perfect to sit and enjoy your morning coffee. Inside you're greeted by the warm and bright living and dining space with vaulted ceilings. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, plenty of storage and a pantry. Unwind after a long day in your private fenced backyard complimented with landscape lighting and flowers that bloom from spring to fall - perfect for entertaining! Need storage? The unfinished basement offers plenty of space along and rough-in plumbing for future expansion! Conveniently located near several parks, including one right up the street, and offers easy access to Highways 34 and 85 for effortless commutes. One year home warranty included! Schedule a showing today! Don't miss the chance to call this your own!
